    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This small figurine is carved from soapstone in the shape of a deity or guardian, facing both front and back to indicate unflagging vigilance. The spell attack roll of any spell cast by activating this item is +13. \n* **Armor** You gain resistance 1 against ranged weapon attacks.\n* **Weapon** When you hit with a Strike using the affixed weapon, or when a spell effect you created by activating the statuette hits with a Strike, you can choose a creature adjacent to the creature that was hit. That creature gains a +1 status bonus to AC until the start of your next turn. No more than one creature can benefit from this each turn.",
        "level": 7,
